SOUL
SOUL COMMANDS
Mimic is a special soul. If you do it alone you mimic whatever soul you just did, or whatever you do when you're just standing around.

 ~CEMOEric mimics himself by staring blankly at the ceiling.~CHLP

But with a person's name (~CCOMMimic felicia~CHLP) it does whatever soul they just did or whatever they're doing when they're standing around.

 ~CEMOEric mimics Felicia by breakdancing.~CHLP

See also: ~CREFsouls
